1. *Voda* je potrebna za život. (Water is necessary for life.)
2. *Vodi* se računa o potrošnji. (Account is taken of consumption.)
3. *Vodu* treba čuvati. (Water should be preserved.)
4. *Vodom* se poljoprivreda hrani. (Agriculture is fed by water.)
5. *Vode* su nam dale neprocenjive blagodeti. (The waters have given us invaluable benefits.)